# --- Source data (downloaded by scripts/ingest.py) ---
# The viewer is data-agnostic. To regenerate public/dataset.json:
#   1. Clone Terminal-Bench 2.1:
#        git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/harbor-framework/terminal-bench-2-1.git data/terminal-bench-2-1
#   2. Download public trajectories from HuggingFace:
#        huggingface-cli download yoonholee/terminalbench-trajectories --repo-type dataset \
#          --local-dir data/hf-cache --include 'data/*.parquet'
#   3. Run: python3 scripts/ingest.py
data/

